<li>Neutrino Oscillations, Masses And Mixing: W.M.Alberico, Torino University&amp;S.M. Bilenky, Dubna NRI; 2003;<a href="http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-ph/0306239v1" class="external free" title="http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-ph/0306239v1" rel="nofollow">http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-ph/0306239v1</a></li>
<li>Bumfiel, Geoff. "The Milky Way's Hidden Black Hole." Scientific American 01 Oct 2001 1-2. 26 Jan 2009 &lt;<a href="http://www.sciam.com/article.cfm?id=the-milky-ways-hidden-bla" class="external free" title="http://www.sciam.com/article.cfm?id=the-milky-ways-hidden-bla" rel="nofollow">http://www.sciam.com/article.cfm?id=the-milky-ways-hidden-bla</a>&gt;.</li>
</ul>
